The liturgical calendar and scripture readings represented in
lectionary_data.json are traditional works of the Armenian Church
(Տօնացոյց / Ճաշոց) and are not claimed as original authorship.

Primary source: the Տօնացոյց (Tōnatsooyts), 4th edition, St. James Press
(Tparan Srbots Hakobeants), Jerusalem, 1915. The readings table was
distilled and cross-year validated during development, with
sacredtradition.am (https://www.sacredtradition.am/) used as a
development test-oracle only; that source is not contacted at runtime and
its raw cache is not distributed with this repository. Where the two
disagree, the printed Տօնացոյց is treated as authoritative (see
dev/source_corrections.py).
